OL,4,Cfollows parents of babies who died
OL,5,Cunder NUH
OL,7,FBabies who died under the care of the
OL,8,Fwill be explored in a new ITV
OL,9,Fdocumentary on Sunday.
OL,11,FThe documentary follows the parents
OL,12,Fjourney's as they struggle to get
OL,13,Faccountability - and to cope with the
OL,14,Fresulting trauma.
OL,16,FBetween 2012 and 2023, 467 mothers and
OL,17,Fbabies died while under the care of
OL,18,FNUH, a figure which doesn't include
OL,19,Fstillbirths.
