OL,3,CITV's 'Maternity: Broken Trust'
OL,4,Cfollows parents of babies who died
OL,5,Cunder NUH
OL,7,FThe film is told through the
OL,8,Fexperiences of a group of families who
OL,9,Fhave campaigned to get answers.
OL,11,FIt investigates failures in maternity
OL,12,Fcare at the trust, which is currently
OL,13,Fthe subject of the largest review of
OL,14,Fits kind ever held in the UK.
OL,16,FAmong the stories told in the
OL,17,Fdocumentary is that of Jack and Sarah
OL,18,FHawkins, who first exposed a failure
OL,19,Fto provide appropriate maternity care
OL,20,Fafter their daughter Harriet was born
OL,21,Fdead in 2016.
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G2/12
