OL,4,Cfollows parents of babies who died
OL,5,Cunder NUH
OL,7,FThey were told her death was caused by
OL,8,Fan undiagnosed infection. But they
OL,9,Fknew instinctively this wasn't the
OL,10,Ftruth.
OL,12,FGrieving parent Jack Hawkins said: "I
OL,13,Fwant to see people in court for the
OL,14,Fdeath of my daughter and so many other
OL,15,Fbabies and mothers."
OL,17,FHe added: "After Harriet died, for
OL,18,Fdays, for weeks, we expected them to
OL,19,Fcome forward to us and say, right,
OL,20,Fthis is the death of a completely
OL,21,Fnormal baby, what has happened here?
OL,1,W~+$ ~sh7}h7sj5 ~{4~k4k4          G3/12
OL,2,W+.! +,*%/"-'"-$/*%/*%/.!T,,,,,,,,,,,,,,
