OL,3,CITV's 'Maternity: Broken Trust'
OL,4,Cfollows parents of babies who died
OL,5,Cunder NUH
OL,7,F"But they didn't do that. It was like
OL,8,Fnothing had happened. Nothing to see
OL,9,Fhere. And hushed, and these things
OL,10,Fhappen.
OL,12,F"They just refused to even have a
OL,13,Fconversation about what else might
OL,14,Fhave happened."
OL,16,FThe couple - who formerly worked at
OL,17,FNUH - subsequently tracked down dozens
OL,18,Fof other families who'd had similar
OL,19,Fexperiences and made it their mission
OL,20,Fto fight for justice.
