OL,7,FTheir campaigning helped pressure the
OL,8,FNHS into setting up an independent
OL,9,Freview, which has now been extended to
OL,10,Finclude over 1,800 families - with a
OL,11,FNottinghamshire Police investigation
OL,12,Falso announced.
OL,14,FThe programme also explores the toll
OL,15,Fof Harriet's death and their
OL,16,Fsubsequent campaign on Jack and Sarah.
OL,17,FAnd, as their fight to improve
OL,18,Fmaternity care across the country
OL,19,Fticks over into years, ever more
OL,20,Ffamilies are joining their group.
