OL,7,FAmong those joining the campaign are
OL,8,FCarly, the mother of Ladybird, who
OL,9,Fsays: "We were told that she probably
OL,10,Fwouldn't survive the birth.
OL,12,F"We decided to end the pregnancy
OL,13,Fbecause we didn't want our daughter to
OL,14,Fsuffer. We found out the test results
OL,15,Fcame back completely clear.
OL,17,F"You can't imagine that feeling. The
OL,18,Fconsultant said you could have
OL,19,Fmiscarried anyway."
