OL,7,FIn a statement, Anthony May, Chief
OL,8,FExecutive of Nottingham University
OL,9,FHospitals NHS Trust (NUH) said: "I
OL,10,Fknow we have failed too many women and
OL,11,Ftheir families, and I acknowledge the
OL,12,Fpain and suffering they continue to
OL,13,Fexperience as a result. For that, I am
OL,14,Ftruly sorry.
