OL,7,F"I recognise the strength it takes to
OL,8,Fshare experiences in the way that
OL,9,Ffamilies have, and I am grateful to
OL,10,Fall those who have engaged with me
OL,11,Fsince I joined NUH in 2022. I am clear
OL,12,Fthat we must listen to women and
OL,13,Ffamilies and act on their feedback if
OL,14,Fwe are to continue our improvement and
OL,15,Frebuild the trust in our services.
