OL,7,F"We have further to go, but the most
OL,8,Frecent Care Quality Commission (CQC)
OL,9,Freport published in September 2023
OL,10,Freflects the progress we are making,
OL,11,Fwith an improved rating for our
OL,12,Fmaternity services. The report
OL,13,Funderlines the improvements we are
OL,14,Fmaking to how we listen to women and
OL,15,Ffamilies, and highlights key
OL,16,Fimprovements in areas such as triage,
OL,17,Fstaffing levels and training, which
OL,18,Fare due to the hard work and
OL,19,Fdetermination of our colleagues.
